{
  "stem": "12053.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And my mother used to, on a Friday, she used to cook and bake all the things in the shop.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And because you were very careful of the, then non-Jews then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They were very. you know, very jealous.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Whatever you cooked-- my mother was a wonderful cook.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She could make some wonderful smelling soup and, and things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I mean, chicken was a rarity.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You didn't have chicken unless it was Yom Tov time, unless it was the festival times.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But anything she cooked, it smelled very nice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the women at work, they had a, an hour for lunch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And she used to bake there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And if she baked one cake, she used to make another two that they didn't know about.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And people didn't have ovens in those days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So you used to send your cakes to the bakers, who was around the corner.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I don't know if you've heard that story before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Very few people had their own ovens for baking in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So my mother used to roll out the cakes quickly and put the-- put everything in it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And it was taken around the corner to the bakers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And in the evening, we fetched it home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And so the workers didn't really know what was being cooked and what we had.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We had to be careful, because the, the people were poor in those days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And it was already the times when they said, the Jews eat like this, and the Jews have that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were non-Jewish, sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my mother always used to give them a taste of this and a-- or a piece of cake and that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they never knew exactly what she cooked or baked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because that was sort of hidden as far as we could.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
